- **Color Palette:**
  - **Primary Blue:**
    - `blue-600` - Primary buttons, links, active states
    - `blue-700` - Hover states for primary elements
    - `blue-50`, `blue-100` - Light backgrounds, badges
    - `blue-500` - Focus rings, accents
  
  - **Neutral Grays:**
    - `slate-900` - Primary text
    - `slate-700` - Secondary text
    - `slate-600` - Tertiary text
    - `slate-500` - Placeholder text
    - `slate-50`, `slate-100` - Backgrounds
  
  - **Borders & Dividers:**
    - `gray-200` - Light borders
    - `gray-300` - Standard borders
    - `border-gray-200` - Card borders
  
  - **Status Colors:**
    - `green-600` - Success, prices
    - `red-500`, `red-600` - Errors, favorites
    - `orange-500` - Discounts, warnings
    - `yellow-400` - Featured badges

- **Background Patterns:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Standard page background
  className="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50 to-slate-100"
  
  // ✅ DO: Card backgrounds
  className="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200"
  
  // ✅ DO: Section backgrounds
  className="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200"
  ```

- **Spacing System:**
  - Use Tailwind spacing scale consistently
  - Common patterns:
    - Container padding: `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
    - Section spacing: `mb-16`, `pt-24 pb-16`
    - Component spacing: `space-y-4`, `gap-4`, `gap-6`
    - Card padding: `p-6 sm:p-8`

- **Typography:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Heading styles
  className="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6"
  
  // ✅ DO: Body text
  className="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600"
  
  // ✅ DO: Small text
  className="text-sm text-slate-600"
  ```

- **Border Radius:**
  - `rounded-lg` - Standard buttons, inputs
  - `rounded-xl` - Cards, larger elements
  - `rounded-2xl` - Hero sections, major cards
  - `rounded-full` - Badges, icons, avatars
  - `rounded-md` - Small badges

- **Shadows:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Shadow hierarchy
  shadow-sm      // Subtle elevation
  shadow-lg      // Standard cards
  shadow-xl      // Prominent cards
  shadow-2xl     // Hero elements, modals
  hover:shadow-xl // Interactive hover
  ```

- **Transitions:**
  - Always include transitions for interactive elements
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Standard transitions
  transition-all duration-200
  transition-colors duration-200
  transition-shadow duration-200
  transition-transform duration-300
  ```

- **Hover States:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Button hover
  className="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white transition-colors duration-200"
  
  // ✅ DO: Card hover
  className="hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-200 cursor-pointer"
  
  // ✅ DO: Link hover
  className="hover:text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all duration-200"
  ```

- **Focus States:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Focus rings
  focus-visible:outline-none 
  focus-visible:ring-2 
  focus-visible:ring-blue-500 
  focus-visible:ring-offset-2
  ```

- **Gradients:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Background gradients
  bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50 to-slate-100
  bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700
  
  // ✅ DO: Card gradients
  bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50
  ```

- **Backdrop Effects:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Glass morphism effect
  bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm
  bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm
  bg-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm
  ```

- **Z-Index Scale:**
  - `z-10` - Badges, overlays on cards
  - `z-20` - Dropdowns, popovers
  - `z-50` - Fixed headers, modals

- **Responsive Utilities:**
  ```tsx
  // ✅ DO: Responsive patterns
  // Padding
  px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8
  
  // Text sizes
  text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl
  
  // Grid columns
  grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3
  
  // Display
  hidden md:flex
  md:hidden
  ```

